  "system": {
    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Stone Lurkers submerge, position under a target using Tremorsense, surface for an Ambush strike, and submerge again. They are slow and hit moderately hard but are genuinely difficult to pin down while natural ground is available. A summoner who places one under an approach path and tells it to hit anything that walks over it will find the instructions followed precisely and without elaboration.</p>"
